  "industry_note": "UNS A03560 / EN AC-42000 / AlSi7Mg / DIN AC-AlSi7Mg — 가장 흔한 cast aluminum (Si 6.5-7.5, Mg 0.25-0.45, Mn ≤ 0.35). 변종: A356 (sand cast, 0.20 Mg high), A356.2 (low Fe), B356 (low Cu). T6 (T7 (over-자동차 휠 (cast wheel), 엔진 블록 (V6), suspension control arm, mil aircraft structural cast. AlSi10Mg 와 거의 동등 (AM 의 AlSi10Mg ≈ casting 의 A356).",
